Package com.msasc.lib.db

Class Record

java.lang.Object
com.msasc.lib.db.Record
public class Record extends Object
A record packs a list of values and their corresponding field definitions.
Author:
Miquel Sas

    • Record

      public Record(FieldList fields, List<Value> values)
      Constructor assigning the list of fields and values. For performance issues fields and values are not validated. In case the construction of the list of values should be validated against the fields, use FieldList.validate(Value[] values).
      Parameters:
      fields - The list of fields.
      values - The list of values.

    • Record

      values - The list of values.
